      "chain_name": "Hardcoded Secret Key \u2192 Webhook Forgery \u2192 Free Orders",
      "attack_scenario": "An attacker extracts the hardcoded PAYMENT_SECRET from the source code. They then call the payment webhook endpoint directly, providing this secret as the auth token, to mark their pending orders as paid without completing actual payment.",
